title: Teens
additional-note: The first issue renewal, recorded in the July-December 1977 CCE Periodicals volume, was filed in October 1976. This appears to be distinct from the 'Teens serial published by Judson Press, but we have found little information about it, and the only issue from this publisher that we have found information on is the December 1948 issue, originally registered for copyright in 1950.
